WEBVTT

00:07.720 --> 00:08.960
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:39.080 --> 01:41.680
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

01:46.040 --> 01:49.520
The Emperor passed away!

01:49.600 --> 01:52.680
<i>The Anping Rebellion came to an end.</i>

01:52.760 --> 01:57.040
<i>In this life,</i>
<i>I cut off Xiao Xun's path to the throne.</i>

01:57.120 --> 02:02.000
<i>But this game to crush him has just begun.</i>

02:02.520 --> 02:05.280
Your Highness, congratulations
on getting what you want.

02:06.400 --> 02:07.640
The same to you, Grand Mentor Deng.

02:07.720 --> 02:08.560
DENG YI, THE GRAND MENTOR

02:08.639 --> 02:10.800
You got wealth and honor
as you had longed for.

02:12.520 --> 02:14.200
The Imperial Guard Commander was involved

02:14.280 --> 02:15.960
and executed.

02:17.160 --> 02:18.200
This position

02:18.760 --> 02:21.200
concerns the entire imperial city
and even the royal clan.

02:22.240 --> 02:23.360
Your Highness.

02:24.760 --> 02:25.640
Anyone in mind?

02:33.920 --> 02:34.760
Jiu.

02:55.920 --> 02:56.920
Your Highness,

02:58.320 --> 02:59.280
what do you mean?

03:00.760 --> 03:02.400
This is my first order.

03:03.280 --> 03:04.640
Fu Jiu, retainer of the Chu Clan,

03:04.720 --> 03:06.200
will be promoted
to the Imperial Guard Commander.

03:07.000 --> 03:08.800
He can be armed at court.

03:10.040 --> 03:11.440
Any objection, Grand Mentor?

03:27.280 --> 03:28.600
IMPERIAL GUARD

03:31.160 --> 03:32.400
Don't regret it.

03:33.320 --> 03:35.240
Don't make me regret it.

03:56.120 --> 03:59.080
General! Urgent message from the Capital!

03:59.160 --> 04:01.240
Urgent message from the Capital!

04:01.840 --> 04:02.760
General!

04:06.240 --> 04:08.040
General, message from the Capital!

04:12.800 --> 04:13.760
THE EMPEROR IS DEAD.
HIS FINAL EDICT NAMES CHU ZHAO AS

04:13.840 --> 04:14.880
GRAND PRINCESS,
TO CO-RULE WITH THE GRAND MENTOR

04:24.440 --> 04:26.960
His Majesty has died. Zhao…

04:28.240 --> 04:29.320
She's the Grand Princess now.

04:30.840 --> 04:33.400
What on earth has she gone through?

04:33.480 --> 04:35.760
Complicated infighting in the court

04:36.360 --> 04:39.680
is far more fierce
than that on the frontier.

04:39.760 --> 04:41.880
At least, she's safe now.

04:43.600 --> 04:45.120
Glad she's safe.

04:47.520 --> 04:49.440
General, enemies are invading!

04:51.600 --> 04:53.560
Arm up! Move out!

05:11.160 --> 05:13.040
TAIJI HALL

05:17.600 --> 05:20.240
His Majesty has arrived.

05:42.480 --> 05:43.480
Zhao.

05:46.240 --> 05:47.120
I want Zhao to be here.

05:47.200 --> 05:48.600
XIAO XUN, HEIR TO THE LORD OF XIAONAN

05:48.680 --> 05:49.880
XIE YANFANG, THE PRIME MINISTER

05:49.960 --> 05:51.160
DENG YI, THE GRAND MENTOR

05:51.240 --> 05:52.240
Your Majesty,

05:52.760 --> 05:54.480
this is inappropriate.

05:56.120 --> 05:58.120
Yeah, Your Majesty.

05:58.200 --> 06:00.200
There is no precedent.

06:00.800 --> 06:01.960
Let the Grand Princess enter.

06:20.560 --> 06:21.920
Yu, what's wrong?

06:22.000 --> 06:24.160
Zhao, I don't want to walk alone.

06:24.240 --> 06:25.640
You walk with me, all right?

06:26.360 --> 06:29.600
If a woman interferes with politics,
the state will collapse.

06:29.680 --> 06:31.360
Please behave, Your Highness.

06:34.120 --> 06:38.120
Chamberlain, don't you remember
what happened before?

06:38.200 --> 06:41.600
When Dowager Empress Xie
ruled behind the curtain,

06:41.680 --> 06:44.000
you were the first to urge
the emperor to take the throne.

06:45.200 --> 06:48.040
Your Majesty, time to move on.

07:00.520 --> 07:03.240
DILIGENT AND VIRTUOUS

07:57.040 --> 07:59.000
Kneel.

08:00.760 --> 08:05.200
Your Majesty, may you have longevity

08:05.280 --> 08:07.880
and a prosperous reign!

08:10.280 --> 08:11.520
Rise.

08:12.400 --> 08:14.680
Thank you, Your Majesty.

08:39.240 --> 08:41.520
Mr. Xie, still here?

08:42.679 --> 08:43.880
I've lingered for a moment

08:44.520 --> 08:48.160
to thank you on His Majesty's behalf.

08:50.480 --> 08:51.720
It's so polite of you, Mr. Xie.

08:51.800 --> 08:54.080
I don't know how I should reply.

08:55.160 --> 08:57.480
You're from the direct line
of the Xie Clan of Gaoyang.

08:57.560 --> 08:59.920
And by blood, you're Yu's uncle.

09:00.440 --> 09:03.960
You can call him
by his nickname in private.

09:06.600 --> 09:08.360
Then let me thank you, Your Highness,

09:09.240 --> 09:12.520
on behalf of my clan, for saving Yu's life

09:12.600 --> 09:14.080
and keeping his throne.

09:14.840 --> 09:16.320
You flatter me, Mr. Xie.

09:16.400 --> 09:19.560
Yu and I will rely on you and your clan.

09:19.640 --> 09:21.480
You're modest, Your Highness.

09:21.560 --> 09:23.360
I know it perfectly well.

09:23.440 --> 09:26.320
You didn't get where you are
by relying on my clan.

09:26.920 --> 09:29.400
Instead, my clan relied on you.

09:30.320 --> 09:31.840
Otherwise,

09:31.920 --> 09:35.760
I wouldn't have had a position
in the court.

09:37.000 --> 09:40.200
Since we're in the same boat,
forget about the formalities.

09:40.800 --> 09:46.080
When we're outside the court,
I'll call you Yanfang. All right?

09:49.280 --> 09:50.560
It's my honor.

09:51.320 --> 09:52.720
After you come back here,

09:52.800 --> 09:54.640
you look very well.

09:55.480 --> 09:58.560
I wonder what illness

09:58.640 --> 10:01.320
made you leave the Capital
for a long recovery.

10:05.280 --> 10:06.880
A long-standing illness.

10:07.480 --> 10:08.920
Thank you for your concern.

10:09.680 --> 10:12.840
<i>In the previous life,</i>
<i>he was best at disguising.</i>

10:12.920 --> 10:16.520
<i>His clan had a century-long history</i>
<i>with profound impact.</i>

10:16.600 --> 10:18.280
<i>To put Xiao Xun off his guard,</i>

10:18.360 --> 10:19.880
<i>he feigned illness and stayed in Gaoyang.</i>

10:20.480 --> 10:24.160
<i>But he secretly gathered private troops</i>
<i>and expanded his power.</i>

10:24.240 --> 10:28.040
<i>A man like him, who keeps a low profile,</i>

10:28.120 --> 10:30.280
<i>is more likely to have the last laugh.</i>

10:34.920 --> 10:36.720
Why do you stare at me like that?

10:37.800 --> 10:39.360
Am I untidily dressed?

10:41.480 --> 10:43.720
I was just thinking…

10:44.640 --> 10:48.680
Yanfang, you're an extraordinary
young man.

10:48.760 --> 10:49.840
Among all the ministers,

10:49.920 --> 10:54.440
I've never seen anyone who could be
even half as smart as you.

10:56.760 --> 10:58.760
I wonder how sincere you are

11:00.080 --> 11:01.360
when you praise me.

11:02.160 --> 11:04.080
Every word I say is sincere.

11:04.800 --> 11:06.760
You're a master strategist.

11:06.840 --> 11:11.480
I'm waiting for you to advise me
on what the Lord of Xiaonan will do next.

11:13.480 --> 11:17.440
The Lord of Xiaonan
didn't mourn the late Emperor

11:17.520 --> 11:19.960
or pay homage to the new emperor.

11:20.560 --> 11:23.240
His ambition is all too evident.

11:24.240 --> 11:28.040
The Grand Mentor has sent nearby troops
to Xiaonan Prefecture secretly

11:28.120 --> 11:30.640
in the name of hunting
remnants of the rebels.

11:31.320 --> 11:33.760
The Lord of Xiaonan
has schemed for over two decades.

11:34.360 --> 11:37.560
I'm afraid a lot of things
are no longer under the court's control.

11:38.640 --> 11:40.440
Can't we strike first?

11:42.080 --> 11:43.480
Not until we have a just reason.

11:44.360 --> 11:47.960
The Lord of Xiaonan declared
he was overwhelmed with grief

11:48.040 --> 11:50.040
and bedridden
over the late Emperor's death.

11:50.680 --> 11:52.360
So, he couldn't come here.

11:53.960 --> 11:55.880
And Yu is his junior.

11:55.960 --> 11:57.120
We must placate him.

11:57.200 --> 11:58.720
What's worse,

11:58.800 --> 12:01.000
foes from the Northern Desert
are lurking on the frontier.

12:02.480 --> 12:04.640
New court, young emperor.
Internal and external troubles.

12:05.760 --> 12:07.880
Our state is too fragile
to survive unrest.

12:08.800 --> 12:10.360
That's why the late Emperor's edict stated

12:10.440 --> 12:12.440
Xiao Xun made contributions
in saving the throne.

12:13.400 --> 12:16.200
Otherwise, his father
might have an excuse for rebellion.

12:17.000 --> 12:19.480
But actually, Xiao Xun
is the mastermind behind this.

12:20.560 --> 12:23.280
He set up the trap to kill
the Crown Prince and Princess.

12:24.120 --> 12:26.120
The Crown Princess is my eldest sister.

12:27.280 --> 12:28.880
She's like my mother.

12:29.680 --> 12:34.160
I'm the mortal enemy
of Xiao Xun and his father.

12:35.040 --> 12:37.440
One day, I'll kill them with my own hands

12:38.880 --> 12:40.320
to avenge my sister.

12:41.640 --> 12:43.320
But not now.

12:43.920 --> 12:46.600
Xiao Xun appears to be the imperial uncle.

12:46.680 --> 12:48.560
But actually, he's still a hostage.

12:49.240 --> 12:52.600
Don't worry, Your Highness.
Take everything slowly.

12:53.320 --> 12:55.120
Do not rush things.

13:01.840 --> 13:02.880
I understand.

13:03.960 --> 13:05.920
Thank you for your instructions.

13:06.800 --> 13:10.200
If you have any further confusion,
summon me anytime.

13:20.600 --> 13:21.680
Be careful.

13:23.920 --> 13:25.200
The paths in this palace

13:27.080 --> 13:27.920
are treacherous.

13:44.200 --> 13:47.160
<i>So, someone like Xie Yanfang,</i>
<i>upright and noble,</i>

13:47.240 --> 13:49.840
<i>also wants to kill people out of hatred.</i>

13:51.560 --> 13:54.000
<i>Since you also intend to oppose Xiao Xun,</i>

13:54.080 --> 13:56.600
<i>then don't blame me</i>
<i>for taking advantage of you.</i>

14:03.200 --> 14:07.280
<i>The Xie Clan of Gaoyang</i>
<i>came to rescue with 5,000 private troops.</i>

14:07.360 --> 14:08.200
<i>It's him.</i>

14:09.440 --> 14:10.360
<i>The Xie Clan.</i>

14:10.440 --> 14:14.080
<i>We heard your mother worked in a brothel.</i>

14:14.160 --> 14:16.280
Our clan doesn't want dirty people.

14:16.360 --> 14:19.560
Since you're just like your mother,

14:20.160 --> 14:22.080
how about we pierce your ear

14:22.160 --> 14:23.600
and dress you up?

14:23.680 --> 14:25.680
Maybe you'll fetch a good price.

14:25.760 --> 14:27.280
You can endure a lot. One more.

14:28.720 --> 14:29.840
Stop.

14:30.440 --> 14:32.880
Uncle, it's really kind of you.

14:32.960 --> 14:35.200
You even pity an illegitimate child.

14:35.280 --> 14:38.640
Xie Xiao, you and your peers
bullied the weak boy.

14:38.720 --> 14:40.400
Do you know how you should be punished?

14:40.480 --> 14:43.400
Do you want me
to take you to the ancestral hall

14:43.480 --> 14:44.600
and make you kneel?

14:45.240 --> 14:47.360
Uncle, we're wrong. We'll leave now.

14:53.400 --> 14:55.480
It hurts, huh? Go get some medicine.

14:57.080 --> 14:58.120
No need.

14:59.280 --> 15:01.040
Your ear…

15:01.120 --> 15:03.000
Why do you wear that?

15:03.080 --> 15:06.320
-If people see it…
-I'm not afraid of being seen.

15:06.400 --> 15:09.560
This will become
part of my flesh and blood

15:10.200 --> 15:13.000
and remind me day after day not to forget

15:13.840 --> 15:14.760
how they pierced

15:15.360 --> 15:16.680
my ear.

15:16.760 --> 15:22.040
And one day, they will be pierced by me.

15:22.960 --> 15:25.080
<i>How dare you rebel?</i>

15:25.160 --> 15:26.760
Your whole clan may be executed!

15:29.080 --> 15:30.840
That's just what I want.

15:31.800 --> 15:32.960
Congrats, Yanlai.

15:35.400 --> 15:37.520
With the Commander's token,

15:38.640 --> 15:39.680
you look impressive.

15:41.800 --> 15:43.520
The Grand Princess

15:44.680 --> 15:47.040
isn't as weak as you think she is.

15:47.640 --> 15:48.960
She's indeed extraordinary.

15:50.880 --> 15:53.680
You worked for Chu Ling for so many years.

15:54.320 --> 15:58.080
You know more about Miss Chu than I do.

15:58.960 --> 16:01.080
She acted perfectly.

16:02.520 --> 16:05.720
But sadly, she's way too impatient.

16:07.040 --> 16:08.480
I'm quite curious.

16:09.080 --> 16:11.320
Why did she suddenly hate Xiao Xun?

16:12.040 --> 16:15.160
How did this engaged couple
become estranged?

16:16.040 --> 16:17.880
Why can't they get along?

16:18.920 --> 16:20.520
From the very beginning,

16:21.920 --> 16:23.880
Xiao Xun wasn't after Chu Zhao,

16:25.000 --> 16:27.120
but the frontier troops
under Chu Ling's control.

16:27.800 --> 16:30.680
She would notice it if she weren't a fool.

16:34.640 --> 16:36.160
It sounds like…

16:38.000 --> 16:39.840
Yanlai, you think she's clever.

16:41.600 --> 16:45.880
I've never heard you
praise anyone else like that.

16:50.480 --> 16:52.160
The way you look at her…

16:54.440 --> 16:56.960
It's like how you look at your pet.

16:58.480 --> 16:59.480
However,

17:00.080 --> 17:02.240
she's a wolf growing up in the desert.

17:03.320 --> 17:04.520
If you're careless,

17:05.280 --> 17:07.520
she'll bite through your neck.

17:07.599 --> 17:10.079
What's bad about a biting wolf?

17:12.200 --> 17:15.839
Isn't that funnier than a dog
wagging its tail?

17:17.760 --> 17:19.440
Yanlai, you know that.

17:20.040 --> 17:21.599
I always like clever people.

17:28.960 --> 17:30.320
I've made my point.

17:31.320 --> 17:34.680
Young Master Xie,
be careful not to get burned.

17:50.800 --> 17:52.360
Thank you for your concern.

17:53.160 --> 17:54.480
When you have time,

17:55.600 --> 17:57.200
come back home.

17:58.160 --> 17:59.200
After all,

18:00.840 --> 18:02.040
you're a Xie.

18:15.600 --> 18:17.920
XIE

18:18.000 --> 18:21.840
XIE YANLAI, THE IMPERIAL GUARD COMMANDER

18:25.240 --> 18:26.320
Now you know

18:27.080 --> 18:29.480
why the Imperial Guard Tally
can't be given to Fu Jiu.

18:30.080 --> 18:33.440
He's a Xie. He's the ninth child
of the Xie Family,

18:34.440 --> 18:35.560
Xie Yanlai.

18:37.240 --> 18:38.360
I know.

18:40.000 --> 18:41.040
You know?

18:43.960 --> 18:46.640
He worked for my father for five years
under a false name.

18:46.720 --> 18:48.360
How could he not be exposed?

18:49.080 --> 18:52.040
You think my father's troops
didn't know his identity?

18:52.800 --> 18:55.520
They did. They just didn't care.

18:56.680 --> 18:58.920
Whether he's Fu Jiu or Xie Yanlai,

18:59.520 --> 19:03.120
if he had ill intentions
or harmed frontier troops,

19:03.200 --> 19:05.120
my father would punish him accordingly.

19:06.760 --> 19:09.360
But you gave the Tally
to someone from the Xie Clan.

19:09.960 --> 19:11.880
Do you know what that means?

19:16.120 --> 19:17.560
Calm down, Grand Mentor.

19:20.560 --> 19:23.320
I can give you more.

19:30.680 --> 19:34.840
Seven shops in Yongfeng Alley
will be put under your name tomorrow.

19:34.920 --> 19:38.280
Glazed cups and glowing pearls
aren't rare.

19:39.000 --> 19:40.480
Two boxes have been sent to you.

19:40.560 --> 19:42.240
Feel free to enjoy them.

19:43.280 --> 19:46.560
If you need anything else,
don't hesitate to tell me.

19:47.240 --> 19:50.400
I'll do my best to get it for you.

19:53.280 --> 19:54.600
Why, Your Highness?

19:56.280 --> 20:00.160
Do you know why the palace walls
can stand for a century?

20:00.840 --> 20:05.360
Because every brick
stays where it belongs.

20:05.960 --> 20:08.360
I made Xie Yanlai
the Imperial Guard Commander.

20:08.440 --> 20:11.160
But I'll count on you for court affairs.

20:12.400 --> 20:14.120
So rest assured, Mr. Deng.

20:14.680 --> 20:16.200
Before I'm no longer the princess,

20:16.800 --> 20:20.040
your position will be rock-solid.

20:24.040 --> 20:25.480
I will

20:26.480 --> 20:28.200
spare no effort.

20:31.880 --> 20:33.120
I've heard your mother

20:34.120 --> 20:35.960
has been missing the hometown.

20:36.040 --> 20:40.000
So I sent men at full gallop
to bring some millet from your hometown.

20:41.160 --> 20:42.200
It's nothing.

20:42.960 --> 20:45.240
Hearing you're a very good son,

20:45.320 --> 20:46.840
I'm just offering a little present.

20:49.120 --> 20:52.480
I… Thank you for your consideration.

20:54.560 --> 20:56.760
<i>Everyone has his weakness.</i>

20:57.480 --> 20:59.520
<i>So do you, Deng Yi.</i>

21:10.240 --> 21:12.440
Xie Yanfang is famous
throughout the state.

21:13.240 --> 21:15.600
<i>But he still can't resist flattery.</i>

21:16.120 --> 21:18.120
Since he likes obedient people,

21:19.200 --> 21:21.920
I'll sheathe my claws before him.

21:22.920 --> 21:23.840
As for Deng Yi…

21:25.800 --> 21:28.320
<i>He's greedy and filial to his mother.</i>

21:29.560 --> 21:30.920
I'll just give him what he wants.

21:36.600 --> 21:38.320
Xie Yanlai.

21:50.400 --> 21:52.520
All the ministers are fierce.

21:53.400 --> 21:54.680
He's the only one…

21:55.840 --> 21:57.880
who protects me with his own life.

22:02.800 --> 22:03.800
XIE YANLAI

22:03.880 --> 22:05.040
Jiu.

22:05.680 --> 22:07.240
I can trust you…

22:08.520 --> 22:09.360
right?

22:33.240 --> 22:34.080
<i>Beat him!</i>

22:34.160 --> 22:35.600
<i>How dare you, an illegitimate son,</i>

22:35.680 --> 22:38.080
burn the ancestors' tablets?

22:38.160 --> 22:40.880
You even angered your father to death.

22:40.960 --> 22:41.920
Believe it or not,

22:42.000 --> 22:44.360
I'll dig your mother out
and feed her to the dogs.

22:44.440 --> 22:46.120
Lowborn! You bring bad luck.

22:46.200 --> 22:47.360
Pah!

22:47.440 --> 22:48.960
Lowborn! Kill him!

22:49.040 --> 22:50.400
Hit him hard!

22:51.200 --> 22:52.760
Beat him to death!

22:53.360 --> 22:55.120
What is he doing?

22:57.840 --> 22:59.560
Are you killing Yanlai, Great-uncle?

23:00.160 --> 23:01.320
Father has just died.

23:01.400 --> 23:03.240
Do you want to lose another family member?

23:03.840 --> 23:06.360
But he burned the ancestral hall.

23:06.440 --> 23:08.480
-Right!
-Without descendants,

23:08.560 --> 23:09.800
what do we need the hall for?

23:10.720 --> 23:12.160
By killing a Xie descendant,

23:12.240 --> 23:13.840
will you answer to our ancestors?

23:13.920 --> 23:16.280
‎HONOR THE CLAN, UNITE THE KIN

23:23.440 --> 23:24.280
Yanlai.

23:29.560 --> 23:30.400
Yanlai.

23:33.120 --> 23:34.920
<i>In childhood, you were afraid of pain.</i>

23:35.880 --> 23:39.600
You cried in the barn
for an hour over your scraped knee.

23:40.840 --> 23:43.720
But today, you endured 18 lashes.
Like a different person.

23:46.640 --> 23:47.840
I'm Fu Jiu.

23:49.040 --> 23:49.880
I'm not your brother.

24:01.520 --> 24:03.040
I remember, when you were ten,

24:06.560 --> 24:08.440
you stole my books to pad the manger.

24:10.440 --> 24:11.960
I chased to the west yard

24:12.640 --> 24:16.920
and saw you wrapping
a crippled dog in the doghouse.

24:17.000 --> 24:19.680
At that time, you said
everything had a soul.

24:20.960 --> 24:22.440
A crippled dog shouldn't be discarded.

24:23.920 --> 24:25.600
But now, what's going on?

24:25.680 --> 24:27.000
When you're discarded,

24:27.880 --> 24:29.840
why do you let their words get to you?

24:29.920 --> 24:31.560
You're just like them!

24:32.760 --> 24:34.560
You look down on my mother and me.

24:35.160 --> 24:37.760
Why are you pretending
to be a caring brother?

24:48.640 --> 24:50.960
I am your elder brother.

24:52.240 --> 24:53.600
I don't need to pretend.

24:58.920 --> 25:00.960
‎XIE

25:28.720 --> 25:31.600
Jiu, you haven't fully recovered.
Why are you on night duty?

25:33.920 --> 25:36.760
It's not appropriate for you
to come so late.

25:39.800 --> 25:42.400
I'm just here to give you a cloak.

25:42.480 --> 25:44.880
You won't reject it, will you?

25:48.640 --> 25:50.080
I'm used to cotton.

25:50.600 --> 25:52.000
I won't like

25:52.720 --> 25:53.840
fancy fabrics.

26:02.000 --> 26:05.240
Cotton is too soft
to guard against arrows.

26:07.480 --> 26:08.640
Don't you agree?

26:10.640 --> 26:11.680
Mr. Xie Yanlai.

26:27.560 --> 26:29.520
Your Highness, are you testing me

26:32.120 --> 26:33.080
or trying to win me over?

26:33.720 --> 26:37.960
I heard when you served under my father,

26:38.040 --> 26:40.320
you didn't bat an eye
when breaking through ranks

26:40.400 --> 26:41.960
and pulled down the flag.

26:43.000 --> 26:44.520
But now,

26:45.200 --> 26:47.320
why are you afraid of a cloak?

26:48.680 --> 26:49.680
Afraid?

26:51.680 --> 26:53.720
Now I have the Imperial Guard Tally.

26:55.400 --> 26:56.520
Shouldn't you

26:59.200 --> 27:00.800
be the one who is afraid?

27:04.560 --> 27:06.040
I am afraid.

27:06.120 --> 27:07.880
Covert schemes are harder to dodge

27:08.480 --> 27:10.680
than open attacks on the frontier.

27:11.560 --> 27:14.160
So, Mr. Xie, will you consider

27:18.680 --> 27:20.160
becoming my ally?

28:08.280 --> 28:10.200
Now, you know who I am.

28:11.120 --> 28:13.240
Why do you think I'll pick your side

28:14.960 --> 28:16.040
instead of my own clan?

28:29.600 --> 28:31.320
Because I'll prove to you

28:31.920 --> 28:34.920
I'm more worthy of your support
than Xie Yanfang.

28:35.600 --> 28:38.080
Is this a deal or an order?

28:49.840 --> 28:51.440
It is a request.

29:05.640 --> 29:06.560
Your Highness,

29:07.680 --> 29:08.720
you're powerful now.

29:09.360 --> 29:11.320
Your request is too much for me.

29:12.640 --> 29:14.680
Let alone the support thing.

29:17.960 --> 29:19.200
You'd better

29:22.760 --> 29:24.080
take the cloak back.

29:42.040 --> 29:45.360
Life is like a chess game.
Nothing is set yet.

29:46.120 --> 29:49.560
Jiu, it's a little rash of you
to reject me so firmly.

29:57.560 --> 30:01.120
If one day, you change your mind,

30:01.800 --> 30:04.600
come to me anytime.

30:32.720 --> 30:33.720
Congratulations.

30:34.240 --> 30:38.880
You've become the Grand Princess
and gained the supreme power.

30:38.960 --> 30:41.600
You can finally take revenge.

30:41.680 --> 30:42.840
No.

30:45.400 --> 30:46.880
I want more than that.

30:47.600 --> 30:49.720
Don't you remember
how Xiao Xun strangled you,

30:49.800 --> 30:51.480
how he cut off your father's head,

30:51.560 --> 30:53.600
and how he annihilated your clan?

30:53.680 --> 30:54.920
Even if you have to lose your life,

30:55.000 --> 30:59.000
you should make Xiao Xun
pay blood for blood!

30:59.080 --> 31:02.680
Nothing but hatred
can get you up to the peak of power.

31:02.760 --> 31:06.280
Nothing but hatred
can make you use everyone,

31:06.360 --> 31:07.480
especially men.

31:07.560 --> 31:10.720
They're greedy for power
and beautiful women.

31:11.640 --> 31:13.320
If you don't mind,

31:13.400 --> 31:15.720
they will do anything for you.

31:16.400 --> 31:20.560
By then, you'll be able
to take revenge without bloodshed.

31:22.400 --> 31:23.520
Revenge.

31:26.600 --> 31:28.000
That's not my only desire.

31:28.080 --> 31:29.960
I do hate Xiao Xun.

31:30.040 --> 31:32.320
I also want to cut off his path to success

31:32.400 --> 31:34.960
and ruin everything he longs for.

31:36.040 --> 31:38.080
To make all this happen,

31:38.800 --> 31:40.280
I have to hide my abilities

31:41.040 --> 31:43.440
and conceal my edge for further action.

31:43.520 --> 31:45.680
With everything you have now?

31:46.280 --> 31:48.720
You're a princess in name only.

31:49.320 --> 31:50.640
Xiao Xun is the imperial uncle.

31:51.240 --> 31:52.720
Deng Yi oversees the court.

31:52.800 --> 31:54.480
The Xie Clan has accumulated merit.

31:54.560 --> 31:55.480
What do you have?

31:55.560 --> 31:57.160
What makes you think you can fight them?

31:58.000 --> 32:00.520
Didn't you risk your life
to become the Grand Princess

32:00.600 --> 32:03.000
just because you wanted Xiao Xun
to regret it

32:03.080 --> 32:07.600
and wanted to slice him
by the blade of power?

32:12.640 --> 32:13.480
No.

32:14.720 --> 32:16.240
I want more than this.

32:19.080 --> 32:20.440
I want to rule behind the curtain.

32:21.760 --> 32:23.480
I want the real power.

32:24.960 --> 32:26.400
I'll make my father and me

32:28.000 --> 32:30.000
live a long life.

32:33.960 --> 32:35.800
What I want is…

32:36.960 --> 32:39.800
Fate won't repeat itself.

32:55.960 --> 32:57.200
What?

32:57.280 --> 32:58.360
Yeah.

32:58.440 --> 32:59.920
The Grand Princess is here.

33:00.000 --> 33:01.280
That's utterly improper.

33:01.360 --> 33:03.200
It has never happened before.

33:03.280 --> 33:04.320
Indeed.

33:06.800 --> 33:08.240
Your Highness, it was all right

33:08.320 --> 33:11.600
that you attended
the enthronement ceremony.

33:12.200 --> 33:15.560
But now, how can you even attend court?

33:16.800 --> 33:19.680
Are you trying to rule behind the curtain

33:20.360 --> 33:22.160
just like Dowager Empress Xie?

33:22.240 --> 33:23.480
That's right.

33:23.560 --> 33:24.480
This is ridiculous.

33:24.560 --> 33:25.760
Outrageous, indeed.

33:27.000 --> 33:28.600
Who does she think she is?

33:28.680 --> 33:29.640
Come on.

33:30.240 --> 33:33.440
Ministers, my duty
is to oversee the court.

33:33.520 --> 33:35.480
His Majesty will rule sooner or later.

33:35.560 --> 33:37.760
His Majesty should attend court.

33:37.840 --> 33:40.240
Who made the rule
that Your Highness can attend court?

33:40.320 --> 33:42.360
Good question, Mr. Qin.

33:42.440 --> 33:43.960
A few days ago, you failed your duty.

33:44.560 --> 33:46.960
By law, you should have been executed.

33:47.040 --> 33:49.960
On the pretext of your military merit,
you were given a minor penalty.

33:50.040 --> 33:53.200
I also want to ask you.
Who made that rule?

33:55.000 --> 33:57.680
We've been sparing no effort
for our state.

33:57.760 --> 33:59.680
But now, in the court,

33:59.760 --> 34:01.320
a woman outside the royal clan

34:01.400 --> 34:04.240
takes charge of politics.
Isn't that ridiculous?

34:04.320 --> 34:05.760
Yeah. That's outrageous.

34:05.840 --> 34:07.200
That's right. That's absurd.

34:07.280 --> 34:08.760
Chamberlain,

34:08.840 --> 34:11.159
you're the father-in-law
of the Third Prince

34:11.239 --> 34:14.120
who killed his elder brother.

34:14.199 --> 34:15.760
If His Majesty hadn't shown mercy,

34:15.840 --> 34:18.960
you wouldn't be standing here and ranting.

34:19.560 --> 34:23.120
Instead of feeling grateful,
you make things difficult.

34:23.199 --> 34:25.840
Aren't you biting the hand that feeds you?

34:25.920 --> 34:28.400
It's perceptive of you, Mr. Deng.

34:29.239 --> 34:32.520
You've figured out everything
about all the ministers.

34:32.600 --> 34:34.360
How admirable.

34:34.920 --> 34:37.960
Within only a few days,
you've put in so much effort.

34:38.920 --> 34:40.960
This is truly a blessing for this state.

34:41.719 --> 34:43.600
When you assist His Majesty so well,

34:43.679 --> 34:46.400
our state will be peaceful.

34:46.480 --> 34:48.400
Entrusted by the late Emperor,

34:48.480 --> 34:50.520
I dare not slack off in my duty.

34:50.600 --> 34:54.120
Mr. Xie, you used to be sick
and away from court for years.

34:54.199 --> 34:56.239
When you're back here,

34:56.320 --> 34:58.320
you must have a lot of confusions.

34:59.160 --> 35:01.800
If you want to discuss anything with me,

35:01.880 --> 35:03.760
I'm always at your service.

35:05.120 --> 35:07.240
Ministers, present your reports,

35:07.320 --> 35:08.840
or the court is dismissed.

35:10.080 --> 35:11.520
But… This…

35:12.840 --> 35:13.920
How could she say that?

35:14.680 --> 35:16.920
What a breach of rules.

35:19.160 --> 35:20.320
Who does she think she is?

35:20.400 --> 35:22.520
She has no right to say that.

35:22.600 --> 35:23.840
She oversteps her authority.

35:23.920 --> 35:26.080
She… She's being presumptuous.

35:26.920 --> 35:28.560
-Yeah.
-Who would accept that?

35:28.640 --> 35:29.680
Yeah.

35:30.280 --> 35:31.320
Commander Xie.

35:35.040 --> 35:36.000
Her Highness ordered!

35:36.920 --> 35:38.160
Present your reports!

35:38.720 --> 35:39.960
Or the court is dismissed!

35:49.160 --> 35:52.000
I… I have something to report.

35:53.120 --> 35:56.920
Recently, I dreamed
that the late Emperor wept blood,

35:57.440 --> 35:58.640
yearning for temple rites.

36:00.080 --> 36:02.680
The late Emperor should
cry out to the current emperor.

36:02.760 --> 36:05.960
Why would a hostage like you
say such things?

36:06.840 --> 36:09.040
In that case, Mr. Xiao must have

36:09.120 --> 36:12.800
a close connection with the late Emperor
because they're blood-related.

36:12.880 --> 36:14.760
But oddly enough…

36:15.320 --> 36:16.400
Mr. Xiao,

36:16.480 --> 36:19.520
why didn't you dream of the Crown Prince?

36:19.600 --> 36:21.400
Does the late Emperor also think

36:21.480 --> 36:25.280
your branch is closer to him
than the Crown Prince?

36:26.600 --> 36:29.960
So, last night, Grandfather
appeared in Uncle's dream.

36:30.040 --> 36:31.840
He must have been angry with me.

36:32.640 --> 36:35.040
In the past few days,
he often came into my dreams,

36:35.120 --> 36:36.960
saying he would fly a kite with me.

36:37.040 --> 36:38.360
But last night, he didn't appear.

36:38.440 --> 36:39.480
Yu.

36:47.440 --> 36:51.640
Your Highness,
what do you think we should do?

36:59.160 --> 37:00.960
Since His Majesty had dreams,

37:01.640 --> 37:06.880
Mr. Deng and Mr. Xie
shall prepare for the sacrifice thing.

37:06.960 --> 37:10.520
We'll do our best.

37:25.080 --> 37:26.960
It's so tiring to attend court.

37:27.040 --> 37:28.520
Can I not go tomorrow?

37:30.000 --> 37:34.200
Yu, an emperor must put the state first
instead of complaining all the time.

37:36.880 --> 37:39.440
-Where's my Nine-ring Puzzle?
-Back there.

37:40.880 --> 37:42.680
Watch your step. Don't trip.

37:42.760 --> 37:43.600
All right.

37:48.880 --> 37:51.640
Without requesting an audience,
I came in here uninvited.

37:52.160 --> 37:54.320
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

37:57.560 --> 37:59.720
You're Yu's close family.

37:59.800 --> 38:01.600
And now I'm his sister.

38:02.200 --> 38:03.640
You and I are close too.

38:04.800 --> 38:08.160
You don't need to inform others
before you visit Yu.

38:08.960 --> 38:11.920
But now, he's the Emperor, after all.

38:12.000 --> 38:15.680
I hope you'll inform me next time,

38:16.240 --> 38:18.600
so that I can be prepared.

38:20.760 --> 38:21.720
I'll keep that in mind.

38:26.040 --> 38:27.120
Yu.

38:32.080 --> 38:33.600
-I'm your…
-Uncle.

38:34.280 --> 38:35.400
Be careful.

38:42.680 --> 38:44.960
You brought a toy to
today's court, didn't you?

38:45.040 --> 38:47.280
It's just a Nine-ring Puzzle.

38:51.680 --> 38:52.640
Give it to me.

38:54.280 --> 38:55.880
I know I was wrong.

39:00.960 --> 39:02.280
Never do it again.

39:10.120 --> 39:11.280
Yu,

39:11.800 --> 39:14.160
this is Mr. Xie Yanfang from the Xie Clan.

39:14.960 --> 39:16.360
He's also your uncle.

39:19.480 --> 39:20.880
Xie Yanfang?

39:22.960 --> 39:24.000
Oh, the Third Uncle.

39:35.600 --> 39:36.520
Yu,

39:38.640 --> 39:41.680
I know you hate my clan and me.

39:42.280 --> 39:45.520
We failed to protect your parents
as well as you.

39:46.160 --> 39:49.360
So, I came here today to apologize to you.

39:51.560 --> 39:54.080
From now on, I'll spare no effort

39:55.160 --> 39:56.360
to keep you safe.

39:58.200 --> 40:01.000
Yu, it's time for morning classes.

40:01.080 --> 40:03.400
Go wait for me in the study, will you?

40:13.040 --> 40:14.200
He's a kid,

40:14.800 --> 40:18.680
and it's normal that he doesn't know
how to hide his emotions.

40:24.160 --> 40:25.960
Don't bother to console me.

40:26.600 --> 40:30.400
We do feel sorry for the massacre
of the Crown Prince's family.

40:31.920 --> 40:33.960
We arrived too late to protect them.

40:35.600 --> 40:37.040
Yu harbors some resentment,

40:38.520 --> 40:39.880
and I understand.

40:41.040 --> 40:42.720
Yu is still young.

40:42.800 --> 40:46.520
After such a tragedy,
his temperament changed somewhat.

40:47.040 --> 40:48.520
Later on, he'll get better.

40:49.880 --> 40:51.120
Next time you come,

40:51.800 --> 40:55.120
bring him some toys,
and that might cheer him up.

41:02.160 --> 41:03.120
How rare.

41:04.760 --> 41:08.560
The two of you match well in character.

41:15.000 --> 41:16.520
How enviable.

41:18.320 --> 41:19.160
Yeah.

41:20.200 --> 41:21.480
Commander Xie is exceptionally brave.

41:22.600 --> 41:23.960
I admire him a lot.

41:24.560 --> 41:27.600
I'll count on him
for the safety of the imperial palace.

41:46.400 --> 41:48.480
You know Xie Yanfang is suspicious.

41:49.200 --> 41:52.040
But in front of him,
you pretended to think highly of me.

41:52.760 --> 41:53.600
What were you up to?

41:53.680 --> 41:55.640
You didn't deny it just now.

41:56.240 --> 41:58.840
So, you agreed
that I was telling the truth.

42:00.440 --> 42:02.200
Does it mean

42:04.360 --> 42:05.960
you've accepted my offer?

42:13.320 --> 42:15.200
It's my duty to protect Your Highness.

42:16.160 --> 42:17.200
Not because of your offer.

42:17.800 --> 42:19.120
Then have you decided?

42:20.360 --> 42:22.280
Once you're the Commander,

42:23.480 --> 42:25.400
you won't go back to Yunzhong.

42:27.040 --> 42:28.280
I was a retainer of your family.

42:30.240 --> 42:31.440
I don't care about that.

42:32.120 --> 42:34.520
As for you, the Grand Princess,

42:35.720 --> 42:37.160
there's really no turning back.

42:45.520 --> 42:46.720
Is this

42:48.480 --> 42:49.680
what you really want?

42:52.600 --> 42:54.880
Xie Yanfang is the head of ministers.

42:54.960 --> 42:56.040
Deng Yi controls speech.

42:56.720 --> 42:59.040
Xiao Xun owns Xiaonan Prefecture.

42:59.600 --> 43:00.680
But you…

43:01.920 --> 43:03.120
What do you have?

43:11.160 --> 43:13.680
I have you, who will risk his life for me.

43:27.320 --> 43:28.920
Two against two. I won't be scared.

43:29.520 --> 43:32.160
Even if Xiao Xun interferes,
we have Xiao Yu.

43:32.680 --> 43:34.240
Three against three, then.

43:35.240 --> 43:36.720
Besides,

43:38.360 --> 43:39.960
you can fight against not only two,

43:41.760 --> 43:43.960
but even a hundred more.

43:57.160 --> 43:59.880
I want you to handle Deng Yi
and Xie Yanfang.

43:59.960 --> 44:03.320
But Jiu, you look like
you want to devour me.

44:12.640 --> 44:13.720
You should figure out

44:14.440 --> 44:15.880
how to handle Xiao Xun first.

44:15.960 --> 44:18.120
He suddenly proposed the sacrifice.

44:18.920 --> 44:20.120
He must have a plan.

44:21.240 --> 44:22.440
I know.

44:22.520 --> 44:23.880
You know?

44:25.280 --> 44:27.240
Then how can you remain so calm?

44:27.840 --> 44:31.080
If I panicked, what would that change?

44:32.440 --> 44:34.400
I prefer to stay put and wait.

44:34.480 --> 44:38.920
I'll see how he's going to play his game.

47:08.720 --> 47:13.560
Subtitle translation by:
